title: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? classSet is not expected
description: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? The output is "MySomeClass".
OB: When calling the ServletContainerInitializer onStartup method with a set of classes, the output is "MySomeClass".
EB: The expected output is not "MySomeClass". The classSet is not expected to contain "MySomeClass".
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Call the ServletContainerInitializer onStartup method with a set of classes.
2. Check the output and verify that it does not contain "MySomeClass".
